overview:
J3 Point-of-Sale designs and sells a point of sale with a complete retail inventory management system designed for retail hardware stores, lumber yards, pet stores, liquor stores, convenience stores and other general merchandise stores or other similar businesses who want to manage their inventory and increase their profits.

Features ranging from electronic signature capture, payment processing, inventory control, to wireless bar code scanning and much more J3 Point-of-Sale sells, installs, and supports point of sale systems all over the world.

Support and maintenance are handled entirely in-house by our expert staff in Ohio, not outsourced somewhere overseas. Easy to learn and use, J3 Point-of-Sale is the perfect solution for any retail business owner. Call 1-888-600-5522

J3 Point-of-Sale is the perfect feature-rich, scalable POS software package for the retail environment. “THE” solution for managing large numbers of SKU’s with the power of QuickBooks Financial for managing your money.
